{"id":102416,"date":"2020-09-16T08:21:58","date_gmt":"2020-09-16T08:21:58","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sleeknote.com\/?page_id=102416"},"modified":"2021-03-09T14:42:14","modified_gmt":"2021-03-09T14:42:14","slug":"countdown-timer","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/features\/countdown-timer","title":{"rendered":"Add Scarcity to Your Campaigns with Our Countdown Timer"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:45%\">\n<p class=\"is-style-preheader\">INCREASE CONVERSION RATES<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h1>Add Scarcity to Your Campaigns with Our Countdown Timer<\/h1>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"925\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-1024x925.jpg\" alt=\"countdown-timer@2x\" class=\"wp-image-102417\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-1024x925.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-300x271.jpg 300w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-768x694.jpg 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-380x343.jpg 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-600x542.jpg 600w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-760x687.jpg 760w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-39x35.jpg 39w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-55x50.jpg 55w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-542x490.jpg 542w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-220x199.jpg 220w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x-385x348.jpg 385w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/countdown-timer@2x.jpg 1202w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Why Use the Countdown Timer?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:6%\">\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\" style=\"flex-basis:42.5%\">\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-04e7e474-eff0-463d-a09f-7bc4ca2e4cbb grids-is-stretch\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-cfa5f6c2-ed11-45ab-9ef3-91a78096e851\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-b222caac-3a0d-4e44-a3cd-c252a694d7b0 grids-is-advanced\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-018ee261-81b1-4374-a1e1-9a47b8883ae8\">\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"http:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Checkmark-1.png\" alt=\"Checkmark 1\" class=\"wp-image-111918\"\/><\/figure>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-4d0db14d-6743-4c73-954a-a6b6b82267c0\">\n\n<p><strong>Create Time-limited Campaigns<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Perfect for Black Friday and other events where you want to offer hourly deals on certain products<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-fccedb67-9efb-4402-997a-6b6903620d65\">\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"http:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Checkmark-1.png\" alt=\"Checkmark 1\" class=\"wp-image-111918\"\/><\/figure>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-3d3aac5d-273b-4a64-930b-03798da175ad\">\n\n<p><strong>Give Delivery Information<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Encourage people to complete their order before the timer runs out to get their order delivered the next day<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-1ae3d14a-3540-4727-9ea3-c8cce8eafee0\">\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"http:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Checkmark-1.png\" alt=\"Checkmark 1\" class=\"wp-image-111918\"\/><\/figure>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-3e6e9ae4-bd9a-43d4-98d1-a6f61cde17de\">\n\n<p><strong>Countdown to Events<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a countdown timer to the promotion of events and let visitors know when registration ends<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:1%\">\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:37%\">\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-52695e40-2042-4429-83eb-623536b12fd4 grids-is-stretch\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-6499b937-a395-4400-93e3-28c1707dab5d\">\n\n<p>It\u2019s no secret: Scarcity marketing works. People always want what they can\u2019t have because they think the grass is greener on the other side.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>How often have you been more motivated by the prospect of losing something than gaining something of equal value?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>More than once, right?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We know this phenomenon as the fear of missing out (FOMO). And it\u2019s highly effective when it comes to getting your site visitors to take action.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In fact,&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/marketingmag.ca\/consumer\/survey-shows-fomo-builds-purchase-intent-139773\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">68% of millennial consumers<\/a>&nbsp;say they would buy something after experiencing FOMO, most often within 24 hours.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>No one wants to feel left out, especially if a good deal is up for grabs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding a countdown timer to your campaigns is a great way to add scarcity to your offers. That means higher conversion rates and more money in the bank.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Countdown Timer in Action<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Here\u2019s how the countdown timer works<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<style>body.sleeknote-theme .sn-quote .auhtor .content strong {color: white !important;}<\/style>\n<script src=\"https:\/\/fast.wistia.com\/embed\/medias\/9kb9lzxi56.jsonp\" async=\"\"><\/script><script src=\"https:\/\/fast.wistia.com\/assets\/external\/E-v1.js\" async=\"\"><\/script><div class=\"wistia_responsive_padding\" style=\"padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;\"><div class=\"wistia_responsive_wrapper\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%;\"><div class=\"wistia_embed wistia_async_9kb9lzxi56 videoFoam=true\" style=\"height:100%;position:relative;width:100%\"><div class=\"wistia_swatch\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;position:absolute;top:0;transition:opacity 200ms;width:100%;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/fast.wistia.com\/embed\/medias\/9kb9lzxi56\/swatch\" style=\"filter:blur(5px);height:100%;object-fit:contain;width:100%;\" alt=\"\" onload=\"this.parentNode.style.opacity=1;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-white-color has-purple-background-color has-text-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-top\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\" style=\"flex-basis:36%\"><div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-2594182a-ff66-47c6-ae94-cdde7cfd8d22 grids-is-stretch\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-07b528f8-db6f-40ea-bba6-554f7f044c8b\">\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:28px\"><span class=\"has-inline-color has-white-color\">Learn How You Can Use Advanced Analytics for Your Business<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div id=\"testimonial-block_5f60ad5159c51\" class=\"block-testimonial\">\n    <blockquote class=\"quote\">\n        3, 2, 1\u2026 Surprise! Want to learn how you can use countdown timer popups specifically for your business? Book a free, personalized demo with me or one of my talented colleagues and we&#8217;ll give you a live tour of Sleeknote (including how you can drive more sales with a countdown timer.) I\u2019m counting the days to our chat\u2026    <\/blockquote>\n    <div class=\"customer\">\n        <div class=\"customer-image\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Jens-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"Jens\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Jens-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/Jens-120x120.png 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/> <\/div>        <div class=\"customer-meta\" style=\"\">\n            <span class=\"customer-name\">Jens<\/span>\n            <span class=\"customer-title\">Head of Sales<\/span>        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\" style=\"flex-basis:45%\"><div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-de4c31a7-23a9-42ce-9c47-c8e358111b05 grids-is-stretch\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-fdc617dd-f052-4dbe-9f0f-40700592bf4a\">\n\n<!-- Start of Meetings Embed Script -->\n <div class=\"meetings-iframe-container\" data-src=\"https:\/\/app.hubspot.com\/meetings\/kj6\/30-minute-11-sleeknote-intro?embed=true\"><\/div>\n <script type=\"text\/javascript\" src=\"https:\/\/static.hsappstatic.net\/MeetingsEmbed\/ex\/MeetingsEmbedCode.js\"><\/script>\n <!-- End of Meetings Embed Script -->\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>How Does the Countdown Timer Work?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>To add a countdown timer to your campaign, you drag the timer into your campaign.<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Then you choose what language and timezone you want the time to show in, and set the time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>You can also style your countdown timer to match the font, size, and color of your brand\u2019s design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, you set a start time and end time, and decide if you want your campaign to disable when the timer runs out, or if you want to show a default message instead.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-fecbcc4b-06f4-45cb-acf7-0324b7d727d8 grids-is-stretch\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-a2a381ad-52c6-4a3a-b189-5a2be526b705\">\n<div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-01f8ec6a-8d08-4eff-b335-faea2b34a22d grids-is-advanced\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-63f9c54a-7b91-4be2-8382-87b9901dbca3\"><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n<div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-0295f779-233b-430b-97bb-fa3b2cc4e544 grids-is-stretch\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-86a388cf-b881-4ce1-91f2-6828f25740f6\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Skyrocket-Conversion-Rates.svg\" alt=\"Skyrocket Conversion Rates\" class=\"wp-image-102286\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Simple Setup<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Drag the countdown timer into your campaign, set the date and time format, and it\u2019s ready to go live.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-0260e952-4e56-46e7-a712-f1208d705047\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Simple-Setup.svg\" alt=\"Simple Setup\" class=\"wp-image-102294\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Automatic Disabling<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">You can choose to have your campaign automatically disable when then timer hits zero.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-1006bbb2-3065-42e0-aca1-a9ffd5abee46\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Real-time-analytics.svg\" alt=\"Real-time analytics\" class=\"wp-image-102290\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Higher Conversion Rates<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Adding a countdown timer to any offer increases urgency and makes your offer more exclusive<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:200px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-ed7cb4e5-3515-49b6-a443-7361823423c8 grids-is-advanced\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-677d6b28-3a7a-4a67-a045-21aa37953ec7\">\n\n<p class=\"is-style-preheader\">USE CASE<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Collect Email Addresses<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re using competitions to collect leads, you can use the countdown timer to illustrate when the competition runs out to increase conversions.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-05a224d2-83ab-4982-a14f-305f54de1c6e\">\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\